headline: Essex Property Trust (ESS): A Fresh Look at Valuation After Upgraded 2025 Guidance
summary: Essex Property Trust (ESS) just made a move that’s turning heads. The company not only delivered its second quarter results, but also decided to raise its full-year 2025 guidance. This kind of announcement usually tells investors that management is seeing stronger performance or better visibility on growth than before, prompting many to revisit their assumptions about future prospects.
